<br>
WHY does Sony so blatently keep forcing us to aa's routes with patch &quot;nerfs&quot; ?<br>
<br>
This is the latest:  Channeling Focus -  I know, the idea is to NOT get hit at all.  We were not built for it, but for some reason, in the latest &quot;how can we Nerf your abilities to ensure you play longer&quot; patch, I can no longer cast trhough any melee without it.  Green mobs that used to interupt me 1/5 casts, now interupt 4/5 times.   Pets I used to be able to cast snare/root on whiloe being hit, now interupt me every time.  (Try fighting a wiz in arena (or anywhere on PvP servers) against a pet class, you'll get the picture real quick).   So now I need to expend 9 more AA's on something to ensure I can cast as before ?<br>
<br>
This patch was a real piece of work.  Wizards are gimped in PvP on multiple levels, DD's do less, now melee's/pets do more.. getting hit from all sides, like the Iraqi Republican Guard.  What was our crime ?  Nerf MB to oblivion.  Do not refund points.  Make melee interupt more.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=laeyakk>Laeyakk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 73<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/11/03 12:44:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25933.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why do we have to spend AA's to maintain power ?</span><hr size=1> Because Verant hates you personally.<br>
